    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-09-03T04:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-09-03T04:35:00-05:00" n="278"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d278">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.20/170: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-09-03T13:00:00+03:25"
                            >September 3, 1942—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received September 3—11:15 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>282. Prime Minister informed me today that he is anxious to obtain the military
                    mission as soon as possible. He asked me to inquire of Department concerning
                    progress being made in this regard.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
